======================================================================
BETA_5 CHECK FOR n=9 TOURNAMENTS
kind-pasteur-2026-03-08-S34
======================================================================

METHODOLOGY:
- Generated 10000+ random n=9 tournaments, found top-H values
- Computed GLMY path Betti numbers beta_0..beta_5 (max_dim=5)
- Used path_homology_v2.py implementation
- Each computation takes 100-300s (SVD of ~2000-3500 dim matrices)

PERFORMANCE:
- Single Betti computation at n=9, max_dim=7: ~115s (original), ~44s (DFS)
- Single Betti computation at n=9, max_dim=5: ~110-290s (varies by tournament)
- Path enumeration is cheap (0.2s), SVD is the bottleneck

H-VALUE SURVEY (10000 random n=9 tournaments):
  H range: [15, 3297]
  H mean: ~1418, H std: ~648
  Top H found: 3297 (regular score (4,4,4,4,4,4,4,4,4), t3=30)
  Second-highest: 3255 (also regular)
  Near-regular tournaments (score (3,4,...,4,5), t3=29) dominate top 20

